### ==========================================================
### Social Service — 12 requests
### Flow: send request → accept → view friends → set visibility
### Note: accept/decline require the OTHER user's token
### ==========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@accessToken = <paste-after-login>
@friendId = <paste-friend-guid>
@habitId = <paste-habit-guid>
@requestId = <paste-from-friend-request-response>

### 1. Send friend request
POST {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/request
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "friendId": "{{friendId}}"
}

### 2. List friend requests (incoming + outgoing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Get pending friend request count
GET {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/requests/count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Accept friend request
# Requires the RECIPIENT's token — paste the friend's accessToken above
# Copy the request "id" from the friend requests list
PUT {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/request/{{requestId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Decline friend request
PUT {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/request/{{requestId}}/decline
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. List friends (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/social/friends?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7. View friend's profile (visible habits)
# Response includes habitsUnavailable: false|true for graceful degradation
# when habit-service is unreachable. habits array may be empty in either case.
GET {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/{{friendId}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Set habit visibility
# Valid values: private, friends, public
PUT {{baseUrl}}/social/visibility/{{habitId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visibility": "friends"
}

### 9. Get all visibility settings (default + per-habit overrides)
GET {{baseUrl}}/social/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 10. Get default visibility preference
GET {{baseUrl}}/social/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 11. Update default visibility preference
PUT {{baseUrl}}/social/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "defaultHabitVisibility": "friends"
}

### 12. Remove friendship (DESTRUCTIVE — run last)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/social/friends/{{friendId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
